property.name: Text 1
property.value: I am the Dark Moloko, released from the "prank" someone called the Zettabyte Moloko Bomb... But, it released me! The strongest Moloko there is! You talking to me must mean you somehow got through the gate I strageticly placed to withold who is unworthy of talking to me. Or someone leaked the password...In which case I shall smite them with my wool I merely use as armor!... Anyways; what are you even doing here? I'm not looking for more followers at this time since our base of operation isn't even set up properly... So uh.. Just go please?
